# Etherscan V2 API keys for Polygon on-chain wallet enrichment (Layer 6).
# Three free-tier keys in parallel give ~9 rps sustained (3 cps each) —
# expected ~3.5 hours wall-time for 109k wallets.
#
# Get keys at https://etherscan.io/myapikey (free tier: 3 cps / 100k
# calls per day per key, verified 21 Apr 2026 on
# docs.etherscan.io/resources/rate-limits).
# Etherscan V2 is multichain: one key covers Polygon (chain id 137) —
# Polygon is confirmed on the free tier. No separate Polygonscan key needed.
#
# Comma-separated, no spaces. Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real keys.
ETHERSCAN_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3
